The paper deals with object recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses semi-supervised learning (cs.LG), transfer learning (cs.AI), and few-shot recognition (cs.CL), which are all related to machine learning. Additionally, the paper mentions using unsupervised metric learning methods (cs.MM) to aid in label propagation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, and cs.MM.
